      • getChildComparator

        protected Comparator<Element> getChildComparator​(Element parent)
        Parameters:
        parent -
        Returns:
        Child element comparator for a specific given parent. This implementation orders Layers top to bottom and ModelElement children using ElementComparator.Factory service with a name matching sort property value before colon, if it is present. If there is no sort property then elements are sorted by label text by default using "label" comparator.
